      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Late summer and early autumn tend to produce the strongest results in Bridgeman Downs. From late January through to March, the family buyer pool that dominates this market is motivated and organised, often with finance pre-approved from decisions made over the Christmas period. Competing stock on the northern corridor has not yet peaked, so a well-presented property faces fewer direct comparisons than it would in the traditional spring window."
      }
